WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.012 --> 00:00:06.299
He had a huge wait list of people who had,
in total, asked for 87 wiper blade sets and

00:00:06.299 --> 00:00:11.549
72 nozzles, but one afternoon things took
a turn for the worse. One of his customers

00:00:11.549 --> 00:00:15.369
called, saying that she had just gotten
contacts and she would no longer be

00:00:15.369 --> 00:00:19.718
needing the wipers or the nozzles that she
had requested. Another person emailed him

00:00:19.718 --> 00:00:23.435
to say that he had gotten laser eye
surgery and he wanted to cancel his order

00:00:23.447 --> 00:00:27.545
as well. Grant was beside himself. Not
only was he sad that he had lost some

00:00:27.557 --> 00:00:32.360
customers, he was frustrated that he would
never be able to target the population

00:00:32.360 --> 99:59:59.000
that didn't wear glasses.

